---
title: Cheesy Pork & Creamy Spinach Sauce with Roasted Potato & Garlic Veggies
description: We've turbo-charged your pork tonight! Special additions like a too-good-to-be-true cheesy and creamy spinach sauce,
herbed spices on the golden chunks of potato and a robust side of veggies are what it's all about. Happy days indeed!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/64ddbd232d1bdde3d94ed896-2b934510.jpeg
